description:
This table, `HereIAmIndication`, logs the state of HereIAmIndication messages from various cells, identifying the location, cell ID, and message attributes.
- `dateTime`: Timestamp of the HereIAmIndication message.
- `Area_Name`: Name of the geographic area where the cell is located (e.g., NR_Balikpapan).
- `CellId`: Unique identifier of the cell reporting the HereIAmIndication.
- `Id2`: Redundant cell identifier (potentially a backup or alternate ID).
- `Id3`:  Additional identifier, possibly related to equipment or location specifics.
- `Id4`: An additional, seemingly constant, identifier (likely not significant).
- `vsDataType`: Type of data recorded (HereIAmIndication).
- `vsDataFormatVersion`: Version of the data format used (Ericsson Specific Attributes).
- `HereIAmIndication.hereIAmIndicationId`: Unique identifier for this specific HereIAmIndication message.
- `HereIAmIndication.hereIAmIndicationState`: State of the reported HereIAmIndication (e.g., ACTIVE, INACTIVE).
